{"tid":2300982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"性侵性虐未成年少女賣片謀利　韓「N 號房」主謀判囚 40 年","createTime":"2020-11-26T03:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T04:36:29.000Z","uid":65328,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"20a2337631f9def52c4fac0f19869836e26d22b2","tid":2300982,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"韓聯社報道，韓國首爾中央地方法院今天對「N 號房」主謀趙主彬被控違反保護未成年人免受性虐待罪行，並營運製造和銷售虐待性錄像而牟取暴利的犯罪集團，判處其 40 年有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n今年較早前，現年 25 歲綽號「博士」的趙主彬，被起訴 14 項刑事罪行。趙被控於去年 5 月至 2 月間組織犯罪活動，在此期間，他與人合謀勒索 74 名女性，當中包括 16 名未成年少女拍攝色情內容，並將其賣給 Telegram 的線上聊天室 Baksabang 的會員，據指聊天室付費會員多達 26 萬名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/ab%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E6%80%A7%E8%99%90%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%B3%A3%E7%89%87%E8%AC%80%E5%88%A9-%E9%9F%93-n-%E8%99%9F%E6%88%BF-%E4%B8%BB%E8%AC%80%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-40-%E5%B9%B4/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2Fab%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E9%259F%2593-n-%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-40-%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F%23&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=d115ca29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2Fab%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E9%259F%2593-n-%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-40-%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F%23&h=b09adc3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/ab%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E6%80%A7%E8%99%90%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%B3%A3%E7%89%87%E8%AC%80%E5%88%A9-%E9%9F%93-n-%E8%99%9F%E6%88%BF-%E4%B8%BB%E8%AC%80%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-40-%E5%B9%B4/#</a>"},{"pid":"b6c31f67ddab9ca74f700814c0b7771a1b0315b6","tid":2300982,"uid":126782,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"是旦啦 咪又係十年後假釋出獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c732ff01d07dc1aff6869138a840ab09a29ae8","tid":2300982,"uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b6c31f67ddab9ca74f700814c0b7771a1b0315b6","tid":2300982,"uid":126782,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"是旦啦 咪又係十年後假釋出獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"重判唔俾佢出黎爆料有份俾錢果班權貴名單"},{"pid":"385a2c7b155bba97f14d09bea87a018d91f8bf05","tid":2300982,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"2018 警察後樓梯強姦14歲女童 判幾耐？"},{"pid":"d85e280b724db65a1a178bd509843e88790be0cf","tid":2300982,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"算短啦"},{"pid":"06b5a3bda16d92a58b9d4c53523d1633424908fb","tid":2300982,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"385a2c7b155bba97f14d09bea87a018d91f8bf05","tid":2300982,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"2018 警察後樓梯強姦14歲女童 判幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:15:30.000Z","msg":"判幾耐都照出緊糧?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50f6e5943f53942ef78a156c62fbb387d937a3e","tid":2300982,"uid":99973,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"睇都未睇過 仲有無link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b714287e2d86d800dd0e8fa7c5b400c9eae627","tid":2300982,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06b5a3bda16d92a58b9d4c53523d1633424908fb","tid":2300982,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"385a2c7b155bba97f14d09bea87a018d91f8bf05","tid":2300982,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"2018 警察後樓梯強姦14歲女童 判幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:15:30.000Z","msg":"判幾耐都照出緊糧?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"更新時間&nbsp;(HKT):&nbsp;2018.08.18 05:20<br />\n【本報訊】一名涉及非禮女童案被停職的毒品調查科警員，上月停職期間相約3名女網友到蘭桂坊夜店飲酒，其後藉詞送其中一名14歲女童返回沙田寓所時，涉嫌在大廈後樓梯強姦對方。警方前日在秀茂坪區把他拘捕，案件交由新界北總區重案組接手，與早前非禮案一併調查。<br />\n早前涉非禮援交女<br />\n<br />\n涉案男警姓余（32歲），停職前駐守毒品調查科。消息稱，余因涉及今年5月一宗非禮女童案已被停職受查，惟有人於7月停職期間，經網上認識3名女子，並相約3人到中環蘭桂坊酒吧見面飲酒，飲得興高采烈。消遣過後，有人藉詞送其中一名14歲女童返回沙田寓所，詎料在大廈的後樓梯強姦該名女童。<br />\n女童稍後返家，其母親發現她有異樣，查問下女童透露曾與人發生性行為，女童母親大怒報警求助。警方沙田警區刑事偵緝人員接報後，翻查大廈閉路電視並根據電話紀錄等，鎖定涉案疑犯，至前日在秀茂坪區拘捕該名停職警員。<br />\n據了解，涉案警員早於今年5月在網上社交媒體結識了兩名未成年女學生，並相約對方在天水圍區見面，其間涉嫌非禮兩女童，當日他正休班。警方事後接獲女童的家長報案，懷疑女兒經Instagram招客從事援交，但從事援交時被人非禮。警方調查後，6月在天水圍區拘捕余，他涉嫌非禮及向年齡在16歲以下的兒童作出猥褻行為，其後獲准保釋候查；余被捕後立即被停職，案件交新界北總區重案組跟進。<br />\n消息指出，警方就早前該宗非禮案的調查已近尾聲，準備提出檢控，未料有人再度涉及風化案件被捕。兩案正由新界北總區重案組合併調查。警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍及姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n■記者黎國剛<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20180818/JVIXQZBJBBUYL4VR7NBQJ2MAAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20180818%2FJVIXQZBJBBUYL4VR7NBQJ2MAAA%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=97825697\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20180818%2FJVIXQZBJBBUYL4VR7NBQJ2MAAA%2F&h=13077467\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20180818/JVIXQZBJBBUYL4VR7NBQJ2MAAA/</a>"},{"pid":"c18a9dd60d7238419ee04c55f63e692f021c8a89","tid":2300982,"uid":55162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:24:07.000Z","msg":"比錢睇嗰班權貴就咩事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cf79ebf47e432219a756f455b13ef3f86c0beb","tid":2300982,"uid":79427,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"點解個樣仲咁招積"},{"pid":"ce2c533d77d90b33eb1bdbf7fbf901e547bcec78","tid":2300982,"uid":73089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9cf79ebf47e432219a756f455b13ef3f86c0beb","tid":2300982,"uid":79427,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"點解個樣仲咁招積"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"知d權貴會救佢"},{"pid":"a53b62fd6900afdbde5ecf56476419e0e35cc381","tid":2300982,"uid":377811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e50f6e5943f53942ef78a156c62fbb387d937a3e","tid":2300982,"uid":99973,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"睇都未睇過 仲有無link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"唔好咁癲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}